  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    SharedPollingConsumerServicePool

    public class DefaultPollingConsumerServicePool
extends DefaultServicePool<Endpoint,PollingConsumer>
    A service pool for PollingConsumer.

    For instance camel-jms leverages this to allow a pool of pollingConsumers so we can support concurrent pollingConsumer in a thread safe manner.
